FBIS4-39033 "drsov108_a_94016" FBIS-SOV-94-108 Daily Report 4 Jun 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Berlin Mayor Stops Russians Participating in Farewell Event Berlin Mayor Stops Russians Participating in Farewell Event LD0406171694 Moscow Russian Television Network in Russian 1600 GMT 4 Jun 94 LD0406171694 Moscow Russian Television Network Russian BFN [From the "Vesti" newscast] [Text] The governing mayor of Berlin has refused to give permission for a brigade of Russian forces to take part in the joint farewell parade of the allied forces, which is to be held on 18 June. His says his decision is based on the USSR-FRG Treaty, according to which representatives of the Berlin garrison of the Western Group of Forces can visit West Berlin only privately.
